block content
  section.pedals-top-section
    .container
      .row-fluid
        .col-sm-6
          h1 Repairs &amp; Mods
          p.well.well-lg.opac Pedal stopped working? Want to squeeze a bit more out of an existing pedal? I can repair or modify most effects pedals. Whether it's a humble DS-1 or a prized vintage Fuzz Face, from simple repair work, to modification, rework, tuning, to sourcing NOS components, I will provide prompt and meticulous work. 
        .col-sm-6
          div(data-isotope-options='{"itemSelector": ".isoitem", "masonry": {"columnWidth": 50, "isFitWidth": true}}').isotope.js-isotope
            img(src='http://distilleryimage10.ak.instagram.com/ab2947623cb511e3855922000a9e0723_8.jpg').isoitem.width2.height2
            img(src='http://photos-g.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-ash/10246017_446786468801254_684868802_n.jpg').isoitem.width-big
