    .container
      .row-fluid
        .col-sm-6
          h4.fa.fa-cogs  Services Include:
          div
            ul
              li Add external power to battery-only effects
              li Clean and renovate that old pedal to keep it gigging into the future
              li Replace broken switches and pots
              li Upgrade components and wiring
              li Add versatility to an existing effect
              li Pedal rehousing
              li Sympathetic restoration of vintage equipment
        .col-sm-6
          h4.fa.fa-spinner  Please feel free to contact me about any work by using the links on the bar below. 
  